After several hours searching for solutions, this is how i was able to resolve the issue.
To prevent scanner.nextLine(); from exiting while loop, You need to duplicate it. Add another Scanner.nextLine(); to the end of the while loop.

    String tex =&quot;&quot;;
    String line;
    while (true) {
        line = in.nextLine();
        if (line.isEmpty()) {
            break;
        }
        tex += line + &quot;\n&quot;;
        in.nextLine()
    }

